    {
      "reviewId": "places/ChIJQ58j_vG3yhQRPWLdfZF6R1Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wc1dWbExhV1EyZURWTk1GOUpXSEpEZW1SUloxRRAB",
      "text": "We had an absolutely wonderful 5 day stay at the CVK earlier this month. This was our second time there, the hotel is in a wonderful location, only a couple of minutes walk from Taksim Square. The service was outstanding, and we had access to the Club Lounge which definitely didn’t disappoint. The food was amazing and the service was even better. Tugay and Berhan were great. Special shoutout to the lovely and sweet Suden! She was absolutely amazing and so friendly and welcoming! Can’t wait to return!",
