    {
      "reviewId": "places/ChIJQ58j_vG3yhQRPWLdfZF6R1Q/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wb05sWjZSa2h3WDJnMmVuaHlhV3hCVWpSRWVuYxAB",
      "text": "CVK was my last stop, and it was the perfect way to end the journey.\nA truly beautiful hotel—spacious, luxurious, and thoughtfully designed. Just sitting on the bed and taking in the details of the walls, the ceiling, and the décor felt calming and indulgent. The garden view from the window added an extra layer of beauty.\n\nThe spaces are generous and elegant, the comfort is undeniable, and the service was outstanding. Every staff member was kind, attentive, and genuinely helpful. It was a seamless, beautiful experience and a memorable ending to the trip.",
