      "text": "From the moment we arrived, the experience at CVK Bosphorus was outstanding. The welcome from the entrance through to the hotel itself was elegant, warm, and incredibly well presented — everything felt refined and thoughtful.\n\nA special mention to Mert at the Stella Bar, whose exceptional service truly stood out. He made us feel genuinely at home and went above and beyond to ensure we had a great experience.\n\nA beautiful hotel with first-class hospitality. We’ll definitely be back.\nFrom the moment we arrived, the experience at CVK Bosphorus was outstanding. The welcome from the entrance through to the hotel itself was elegant, warm, and incredibly well presented — everything felt refined and thoughtful.\n\nA special mention to Mert at the Stella Bar, whose exceptional service truly stood out. He made us feel genuinely at home and went above and beyond to ensure we had a great experience.\n\nA beautiful hotel with first-class hospitality. We’ll definitely be back.",
